* Integration Tests
** Purpose
***_ Validate component interactions
***_ Verify data flows correctly
** Characteristics
***_ Use actual Databricks resources
***_ Test schemas and data types
***_ More setup than unit tests
** Test Environment
***_ Dedicated test schemas/catalogs
***_ Representative data samples
***_ Isolated from production
** Rule
***_ Never run against production tables
***_ Separate test environment required
@endmindmap
